\square ABCD
d
|BD| = d \sin A = d \sin C \qquad |AC| = d \sin B = d\sin D
\begin{align} ps+ qr &= \frac{2}{|BD|/d} \left(\; \frac{1}{2} p s \sin A + \frac{1}{2} qr \sin C \;\right) \\[4pt] &= \frac{2d}{|BD|} \left( |\triangle BAD| + |\triangle BCD| \right) \\[4pt] &= \frac{2d |\square ABCD|}{|BD|} \\[6pt] pq+rs &= \frac{2d|\square ABCD|}{|AC|} \end{align}
\frac{ps+qr}{pq+rs} = \frac{|AC|}{|BD|}
